[
    {
        "text": "An enduring myth says we use only 10% of our brain,...",
        "startTime": 111,
        "endTime": 3182,
        "slowStartTime": 317,
        "slowEndTime": 4998
    },
    {
        "text": "...the other 90% standing idly by for spare capacity.",
        "startTime": 3505,
        "endTime": 6905,
        "slowStartTime": 5407,
        "slowEndTime": 10583
    },
    {
        "text": "Hucksters promised to unlock that hidden potential...",
        "startTime": 7487,
        "endTime": 10087,
        "slowStartTime": 11380,
        "slowEndTime": 15355
    },
    {
        "text": "...with methods based on neuroscience, but all they really unlock is your wallet.",
        "startTime": 10388,
        "endTime": 15107,
        "slowStartTime": 15732,
        "slowEndTime": 22885
    },
    {
        "text": "Two-thirds of the public and nearly half of science teachers mistakenly believe the 10% myth.",
        "startTime": 15834,
        "endTime": 21293,
        "slowStartTime": 23901,
        "slowEndTime": 32164
    },
    {
        "text": "In the 1890s, William James, the father of American psychology, said,...",
        "startTime": 21759,
        "endTime": 26122,
        "slowStartTime": 32789,
        "slowEndTime": 39408
    },
    {
        "text": "...\"Most of us do not meet our mental potential.\"",
        "startTime": 26457,
        "endTime": 28604,
        "slowStartTime": 39835,
        "slowEndTime": 43131
    },
    {
        "text": "James meant this as a challenge, not an indictment of scant brain usage.",
        "startTime": 29273,
        "endTime": 33106,
        "slowStartTime": 44059,
        "slowEndTime": 49884
    },
    {
        "text": "But the misunderstanding stuck.",
        "startTime": 33539,
        "endTime": 35075,
        "slowStartTime": 50459,
        "slowEndTime": 52837
    },
    {
        "text": "Also, scientists couldn't figure out for a long time the purpose of our massive frontal lobes...",
        "startTime": 35621,
        "endTime": 40957,
        "slowStartTime": 53582,
        "slowEndTime": 61660
    },
    {
        "text": "...or broad areas of the parietal lobe.",
        "startTime": 41216,
        "endTime": 43362,
        "slowStartTime": 61974,
        "slowEndTime": 65268
    },
    {
        "text": "Damage didn't cause motor or sensory deficits,...",
        "startTime": 43750,
        "endTime": 46422,
        "slowStartTime": 65775,
        "slowEndTime": 69858
    },
    {
        "text": "...so authorities concluded they didn't do anything.",
        "startTime": 46761,
        "endTime": 49493,
        "slowStartTime": 70291,
        "slowEndTime": 74464
    },
    {
        "text": "For decades, these parts were called silent areas, their function elusive.",
        "startTime": 50216,
        "endTime": 54297,
        "slowStartTime": 75474,
        "slowEndTime": 81670
    },
    {
        "text": "We've since learned that they underscore executive and integrative ability,...",
        "startTime": 54737,
        "endTime": 58263,
        "slowStartTime": 82256,
        "slowEndTime": 87620
    },
    {
        "text": "...without which we would hardly be human.",
        "startTime": 58631,
        "endTime": 60347,
        "slowStartTime": 88097,
        "slowEndTime": 90745
    },
    {
        "text": "They're crucial to abstract reasoning, planning, weighing decisions...",
        "startTime": 60879,
        "endTime": 64231,
        "slowStartTime": 91468,
        "slowEndTime": 96571
    },
    {
        "text": "...and flexibly adapting to circumstances.",
        "startTime": 64521,
        "endTime": 66779,
        "slowStartTime": 96932,
        "slowEndTime": 100394
    },
    {
        "text": "The idea that nine-tenths of your brain sits idly by in your skull...",
        "startTime": 67401,
        "endTime": 70955,
        "slowStartTime": 101252,
        "slowEndTime": 106657
    },
    {
        "text": "...looks silly when we calculate how the brain uses energy.",
        "startTime": 71192,
        "endTime": 74199,
        "slowStartTime": 106938,
        "slowEndTime": 111523
    },
    {
        "text": "Rodent and canine brains consume 5% of total body energy.",
        "startTime": 74655,
        "endTime": 78909,
        "slowStartTime": 112132,
        "slowEndTime": 118589
    },
    {
        "text": "Monkey brains use 10%.",
        "startTime": 79325,
        "endTime": 80777,
        "slowStartTime": 119138,
        "slowEndTime": 121390
    },
    {
        "text": "An adult human brain, which accounts for only 2% of the body's mass,...",
        "startTime": 81306,
        "endTime": 85311,
        "slowStartTime": 122109,
        "slowEndTime": 128191
    },
    {
        "text": "...consumes 20% of daily glucose burned.",
        "startTime": 85606,
        "endTime": 88969,
        "slowStartTime": 128559,
        "slowEndTime": 133678
    },
    {
        "text": "In children, that figure is 50% and in infants, 60%.",
        "startTime": 89437,
        "endTime": 93865,
        "slowStartTime": 134305,
        "slowEndTime": 141023
    },
    {
        "text": "This is far more than expected for their relative brain sizes,...",
        "startTime": 94561,
        "endTime": 97584,
        "slowStartTime": 141992,
        "slowEndTime": 146601
    },
    {
        "text": "...which scale in proportion to body size.",
        "startTime": 97851,
        "endTime": 99799,
        "slowStartTime": 146926,
        "slowEndTime": 149923
    },
    {
        "text": "Human ones weigh 1.5 kilograms, elephant brains 5 kilograms and whale brains 9 kilograms,...",
        "startTime": 100291,
        "endTime": 106171,
        "slowStartTime": 150587,
        "slowEndTime": 159482
    },
    {
        "text": "...yet on a per weight basis, humans pack in more neurons than any other species.",
        "startTime": 106434,
        "endTime": 111694,
        "slowStartTime": 159801,
        "slowEndTime": 167766
    },
    {
        "text": "This dense packing is what makes us so smart.",
        "startTime": 112046,
        "endTime": 114533,
        "slowStartTime": 168219,
        "slowEndTime": 172025
    }
]